<D>__{i realize that you're mad at me }
<C>__{terry}
<P>__{(deadpan)}
<D>__{i'm not mad at you...}
<C>__{sammy}
<D>__{ but he didn't do anything to you. and you cannot promise a little boy that you're gonna }
<C>__{terry}
<P>__{(on "boy")}
<D>__{...i just, you know, after all that religious conversation, i just realized it's probably not so good for him to be spending so much time with someone like me who doesn't believe his life is important in the scheme of things }
<C>__{sammy}
<D>__{would you please...}
<C>__{terry}
<D>__{i'm serious.}
<C>__{sammy}
<P>__{(practically choking)}
<D>__{listen.}
<P>__{(pause)}
<D>__{i am sure, if you put your mind to it, you can think of some other way of getting back at me besides this. so would you please just give it some thought, and take him fishing tomorrow?}
